body.name: Front and Inside Dash Camera, LAMONKE 4K/2160P Car Camera, Dashcam with WiFi, GPS, Smart APP Control, IR Night Vision Dashcam, 24/7 Recording Parking Mode, G-Sensor, WDR, up to 256GB SD Support.
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Thursday, February 22. Order within 1 hr 6 mins
features: 【4K ULTRA HD DUAL RECORDING】The LAMONKE dash cam features a SONY STARVIS IMX 335 Sensor, and Novatek Chip to capture the road ahead and inside your car in resolutions up to Ultra HD 4K(3840*2160P) and FHD 1080P simultaneously. It reads most details from street signs, license plates, passenger compartments, etc, providing essential evidence of driving situations and protecting you from traffic disputes and fraud, such as sudden collisions, pulling over, sudden queue jumping, or passenger disputes

【INBUILT 2.4GHZ WiFi & OPTIONAL GPS】The dash cam connects to your phone with inbuilt 2.4Ghz WiFi and brings faster data transfer speed, ensuring you access videos/photos, manage some camera settings, download and share your footage on the free Roadcam app. The GPS module provides GPS information on driving route, vehicle's speed, distance, position, real time, and maps on the computer, which can be used as evidence if you are convicted of a speeding violation or get into a traffic accident

【PLUG AND PLAY & LOOP RECORDING DASH CAM】The dash cam is power supplied from the cigarette lighter port. After inserting the sd card, the dashcam will power on and record automatically when your car turns on. With the loop recording function, the dash cam will automatically overwrite the earliest unlocked videos when the sd card is full to achieve 24/7 continuous recording. Please kindly note that the dash cam supports 256 GB micro sd card max( U3 Level, sd card is NOT included)

【WDR & NIGHT VISION INTERIOR CAR CAMERA】The dash cam interior car camera with 4 infrared LED lights and a 140 degree inside view angle, which can accurately capture the driver and passengers in low light and effectively deal with the passenger dispute. The upgraded 4K front-facing dash camera lens adopts WDR technology to auto-balance the light and dark areas, with a 170 degree wide view angle that covers most lanes of traffic, reducing the blind spots and recording clearly even at night

【EXTENDED WARRANTY & OPTIONAL GIFT】The package comes with the 4k dual dash cam, car charger with GPS module, mounting suction cup, user guide, and 12-month warranty. Worry-free 30 days money-back policy for any initial defect on the dashcam. Even if it exceeds 30 days, we will accept re-shipment. If you have any issues, please contact us.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The Roadcam app is a Free app. Available for Android and iOS. You can playback, download and share the recorded videos on the app.Once the dashcam is controlled by the app, you need to disconnect the wifi first, then control the dashcam manually, if it is stuck, please try to restart the dash cam.For Any wifi or app issues, please be kind to let us know it.

The dash cam supports 256GB Micro Sd Card Max. The memory card is NOT included in the packaging. If you need replace the sd card, Please use the Class 10, U3 High-Speed Micro-SD Card for 4K Video, which are made for 4K high-end dashcam. Please DON’T USE any “SanDisk Ultra” or "Generic Class 10 for HD Video" Cards from third-party sellers.Please formate the sd card when first use, If you have any sd card issues, please let us know it.The emergency recorded video is the protected video, need delete it manually. If the sd card get full quickly, please adjust the level of the gravity sensor as "LOW" or "Medium"

You can choose to turn off the inside dash cam, it will not influence the resolution of the front camera.3 Options for dash cam display: 4K(Front Only), 4K(Front)+1080P(Inside), 2K(Front)+1080P(Inside)The dash cam will suitable for the most 12V car types, Not suitable for Trucks (24V)If the dash cam turn on/off frequently, please check the connection of power supply or replace a Class 10, U3 High-Speed Micro-SD Card.

Real 4K Dual Camera The real 4k dual dash cam can record the driving status of the car front and car inside up to 4k and 1080p resolution. With an advanced Sony IMX 335 sensor, details can be clearly recorded in your dash cam, offering essential evidence for accident claims. Fatigue Driving Reminder LAMONKE always cares about your health and car safety. With this humanized function of fatigue driving reminder, you can set the time to remind you to take a rest or cheer you after a long time driving. The dash cam will beep when the time is up. Screen Saver & Clock The dash cam can turn off the screen display to not block the driver's attention but still keep recording. And it can also be used as a clock to show the time instead of a black screen when you turn on the function of the time display at the same time. WDR Night Vision LAMONKE dashcam also features a good performance of night vision. With the WDR technology and 4 IR lights, the dash cam can balance the brightness and supply light for low light conditions and night, clearly recording the details of night driving.

Basic Specifications of LAMONKE 4K Dual Dash Cam Video Resolution 4K ( Front )+1080P(Inside), Adjustable App RoadCam (Free app), Manage camera settings and files, share videos to social medias on your phone WiFi 2.4Ghz WiFi Only, The available distance of the WIFI connection is 9-15ft, and it will be automatically disconnected if out of the range. GPS Information Support on PC Loop Recording OFF/1 /3 /5 minutes G-sensor High/Medium/Low sensitivity Parking Monitor On/Off, (If you need the 24 hours parking monitor, you need equip with the external power supply or hardwire kit ( NOT INCLUDED) Motion Detection On/Off, works when the dash cam is on WDR On/Off Fatigue Driving Reminder Off/1/2/3/4 hours Night Vision On/Off, IR interior car dash cam Screen Saver/Clock Display OFF/30s/1 minute/3 minutes, Still recording the footage SD Card Supported 256GB, Not includes SD Card, please use U3 level high-speed sd card Certified Certified: CE, FCC, RoHS Package Includes 1X 4K Dual Dash Cam; 1X Car Charger with GPS Antenna; 1X Suction Cup; 1X User Manual Languages English, Japanese, German, Italian, French, Spanish

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quality is good
reviews.reviewText: I replaced my old camera with this new one. The 4K is good, I can see the picture is very clear and able to capture the number on the car. It’s easy to install but a little bit hard to connect the WiFi, so far it is nice camera with good looking!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice little dashcam !
reviews.reviewText: I was originally looking for just the front-facing dash cam but the passenger recording feature is a nice add-on. I've used it for a couple of weeks now and my experience has been great. I've it mounted on my dash instead of the windshield and it records great videos. Not only does it record incidents but also great videos in general during your road trips. The night vision is crisp and clear. Loop recording is standard . My favorite feature is the app and wifi and it enables saving videos, GPS features, and 24-hour monitoring especially any incidents while the vehicle is parked, etc. recommend this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It doesn’t need running cable to the back trunk
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I used to have those single camera system but it won’t take the back road condition of my car. If anything happen at the back that this front only recording is useless. Two camera system is good but you need to pay a pro to run the cable to the back trunk and drill a hole for camera lens. Until this model that has build-in two camera that I really like, I can just remove the center headset piece the the back view is easily recorded into high res 4K video I’m very impressed the quality!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Camara de carro.
reviews.reviewText: Muy buena la cámara, se las recomiendo.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This camera is awesome and super easy to navigate
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This camera is super easy to use and navigate, it's got an awesome picture during the day and night. You can clearly see the license plate of the car in front of you and downloading a video to your phone could not be easier.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Won't stay on mount
reviews.reviewText: The Camera itself isn't terrible, the huge issue is that the slot where the camera attaches to the mount arm is absolute trash!If you hit a speed bump or brake to hard it will come loose and dangle from the cord.This started happening much more frequently until after the return window, otherwise I would have gotten rid of the thing.Also I cannot figure out how to convert the reading from kilometers to miles per hour, if it even has that option?Would not recommend if you want a study dash cam.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This dashcam comes with everything that I need
reviews.reviewText: This cam comes with dual viewing/ display: outside the car and inside the inside the car too which I can to peek on my sons who sit behind me from little of the angle. Not to mention it can also record the voice, I can’t wait to record the moment of my trip which my family love to sing together in the car.The loop recording comes with 3 different durations so I can set it according how I like it. The quality of the recoding is better than my previous dashcam that I got a year and half ago.Highly recommend it, I think I need to get another one for my dad too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Bought one had to return it. It did not work at all go the second one the setting button did not work. Had to return both got my money back . Thanks Amazon for the quick return.

reviews.reviewTitle: 前後カメラとも広角で明るいレンズで、さらにFullHD対応。GPS、SDカード付で3年保証、総合的コスパは上々
reviews.reviewText: 5年ほど前に買ったドラレコが不具合で使えなくなった為、買い換えました。前後カメラ付き、F1.8の明るいレンズ、良いセンサー、邪魔にならないサイズ、GPS機能組み込み済み、前後ともFullHD録画対応、SDカード付、保証期間3年と、中国メーカー品と比べても価格も悪くないと判断し購入しました。※中国メーカーはGPSが別売りだったり、4Kとうたっていても結局前後同時はFullHDだったりと 同じレベルの物をそろえようとするとコストは大して変わらないと思います。取り付けて映像確認しましたが前後カメラとも十分な画質で撮影できていると思います。マウント部は噛み合わせで山谷が合わさるような構造になっていて、カメラの方向を決定してネジ締めをしたら、カメラも一緒にまわってしまい位置決めがズレることがありません。また、この噛み合わせのおかげで多少ネジが緩んでも簡単には位置ズレしません。この辺の構造的配慮は有難いと思いました。実際の耐久性についてはこれから継続しなければわかりませんが、使用開始した現状で不安になるようなものは有りません。もし何かあっても、3年保証の安心感があります。各種支援機能については不要の為、未評価です。中国メーカー品によくあるWifi機能はこの製品には付いていませんが、問題が起きなければ、ドラレコの映像を見る場面などありませんし、いざ問題が起きても、映像をその場で見て決着などあり得ないので問題ないです。なにか必要になったら普通のカメラ同様にPCに接続して吸い出すだけです。
作りも良く機能も充実して大変良い
大手メーカーだけあって何も問題なく取り付け出来ましたただ後方のカメラの配線を何処を通すか悩みました
自分で取り付けました。画像も悪くないかと思います。後は、どのくらい耐久性があるかどうか。取り付けて一ヶ月ではなにもなし。
ニュースであおりや事故を見て、家人が付けるよう言うので購入ディラーで商品を持参してもらったら取り付けますよと言われていたのでアマゾンで口コミを見て購入して取り付け（工賃￥46.000円は普通ですか？ 某BMW）付けてからの感想は、道路のちょっとした凸凹ですぐに反応する感度を弱くしたら駐車中のコッンに反応しない按排が難しい
